{"tid":1501594,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"獲澳門新聞局批准採訪特首選舉 《蘋果》記者「企圖危害公共安全」被拒入境","createTime":"2019-08-24T11:50:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T14:53:24.000Z","uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ab341bbfe1bfdf61a9354a34fcdd8755f9da20d8","tid":1501594,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:50:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190824/large/1566643112_a92f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190824%2Flarge%2F1566643112_a92f.png&h=c3043819&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n澳門明日舉行特首選舉，在僅得一名候選人參選情況下，選戰已成定局。惟澳門當局今日加緊出入境審查，《蘋果》一名已獲當地新聞局批准採訪的記者，今日中午入境澳門時被拒絕入境。在扣查期間，記者表明赴當地採訪，澳門治安警最後以「企圖入境澳門從事危害澳門公共安全或公共秩序活動」為由，拒絕記者入境，惟警員未有解釋為何採訪會危害澳門公共安全。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》派出兩名記者採訪澳門特首選舉，早前向澳門新聞局報名，並已獲新聞局批准採訪申請。二人今日中午乘船前往澳門，下午1時45分抵達澳門外港碼頭，於入境櫃位辦理入境手續時，兩人均被關員截停，被帶到當地治安警房間調查。當時房間內有多名港人被截查，年齡普遍界乎20至30歲。<br />\n<br />\n調查期間，治安警多次查問記者入境目的。《蘋果》記者清楚表明，已向澳門新聞局報名參與採訪，並獲回覆批准，同時向關員展示記者證。治安警隨後要求記者到海關的房間，搜查隨身物品。經過接近2個小時扣查後，最終只有一名記者獲准入境。<br />\n<br />\n另一名記者則被澳門當局發出拒絕入境通知書，通知書原因一欄列出「存有強烈跡象顯示，利害關係人企圖入境澳門從事危害澳門公共安全或公共秩序活動」，故引用《內部保安綱要法》拒絕入境。惟治安警全程「照稿讀」，拒絕解釋為何採訪活動是危害澳門公共安全或公共秩序的活動。隨後記者被遣返回港，據記者觀察同船有兩名內地女子，亦被拒入境折返香港。另有一名陳姓網媒記者，今早於外港碼頭被關員截查後，決定放棄入境自行回港。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190824/59969674?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190824%2F59969674%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOpNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=48bdfcf5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190824%2F59969674%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=e1ddd55e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190824/59969674?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"ddaf7321981efcaf6e24c7a2b9e287914ec2b738","tid":1501594,"uid":224561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:04:54.000Z","msg":"唔去都罷啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e566a696859e950c26173dc1febe5d74a7bbe91","tid":1501594,"uid":78304,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:15:26.000Z","msg":"中國唔去都罷"},{"pid":"77a924b7b15d4d5612a8a966da09cb71fcad933f","tid":1501594,"uid":221265,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:17:32.000Z","msg":"其實澳門早喺60年代就淪陷"},{"pid":"239bf058eb3d54d446dd93f03c3d851af80403f7","tid":1501594,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:18:50.000Z","msg":"Macau popo is also popo"},{"pid":"c981d44e46c606357953443cb1cbbd87b5e286ff","tid":1501594,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:30:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以證實佢新聞處係獨立機構"},{"pid":"4919da76e24a3dd64697961106f05a7d2fe7cce6","tid":1501594,"uid":262093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:53:24.000Z","msg":"唔好過嚟澳門啦，大家留返喺香港戰鬥啦。"}]}